            "pathId": -6870764566816255341,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "メジロパーマー",
            "enName": "Mejiro Palmer",
            "jpText": "とまぁ、そんなワケだから……。\nどれにするか悩んじゃってさ～。",
            "enText": "And that's why… is the best. I couldn't \ndecide which one to choose.",
